<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Banking System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="logo" href="/"><span>AVK BANK</span></a>
            <img id="mobile-cta" class="mobilebutton" src="menu.svg" alt="menu button mobile">
            <nav>
                <img id="mobile-exit" class="mobilebutton-exit" src="menu.svg" alt="menu button mobile exit">
                <ul class="pri-nav">
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="Accounts.ejs">Accounts</a></li>
                    <li><a href="MoneyTransfer.ejs">Money Transfer</a></li>
                    <li><a href="TransactionHistory.ejs">Transaction History</a></li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="sec-nav">
                    <li><a href="FAQ.ejs">FAQ</a></li>
                    <li><a href="Contact.ejs">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>


     <script>
         const mobilebtn = document.getElementById('mobile-cta')
               nav = document.querySelector('nav')
               mobilebtnexit = document.getElementById('mobile-exit');
        mobilebtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            nav.classList.add('menu-btn');
        })
        mobilebtnexit.addEventListener('click', () => {
            nav.classList.remove('menu-btn');
        })

     </script>

     <div class="faq">
         <h3 class="q1">How To Transfer the Money?</h3>
         <p class="a1">Click on Money Transfer in the Navigation Bar and Fill the Details to whom you want to transfer. </p>
         <h3 class="q2">How to check whether our Transaction is done?</h3>
         <p class="a2">Check in the Transaction history page for recent transactions.</p>
         <h3 class="q3">How to check our Account Balance?</h3>
         <p class="a3">Go to the Accounts page and check out your balance.</p>
         <h3 class="q4">How to apply for a New Account?</h3>
         <p class="a4">Send a Mail to Us mentioning details of the particular person.</p>
         <h3 class="q5">What to do if wrong transaction was made?</h3>
         <p class="a5">Immediately call us at our Toll Free Number and register a complaint.</p>
         <h3 class="q6">How to contact AVK BANK?</h3>
         <p class="a6">Check our contact page.</p>
     </div>

</body>
</html>